Subject: [PATCH] usb: dwc3: move synchronize_irq() out of the spinlock
 protected block
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.1.6
Git-commit: 41a91c606e7d2b74358a944525267cc451c271e8

[ Upstream commit 41a91c606e7d2b74358a944525267cc451c271e8 ]

